# Pinned JDK for SDKMAN! users. Run `sdk env install` once on a fresh clone so the shell
# matches the Gradle toolchain (foojay resolves the same version inside the build, but
# JAVA_HOME drives keytool, the Kotlin daemon, and adb-launched processes).
#
# CI parity target per docs/adrs/ADR-001-stack-and-build-infra.md and scripts/doctor.sh:
# JDK 25, Android SDK platform 35, Gradle wrapper 9.1.0.
java=25.0.1-tem
